## ğŸ§© Advanced: Custom Package Structure

### ğŸ“ Folder Structure:
```
my_project/
â”‚
â”œâ”€â”€ analytics/
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ __init__.py
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ stats.py
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ trends.py
â”‚
â””â”€â”€ main.py
```

### âœ… `stats.py`:
```python
def mean(data):
    return sum(data) / len(data)
```

### âœ… `main.py`:
```python
from analytics.stats import mean

print(mean([10, 20, 30]))  # Output: 20.0
```

